'''William Hedgcock''' (July 4, 1883 &ndash; September 29, 1947) was an American [[audio engineering|sound engineer]]. He was nominated for an [[Academy Award]] for [[Academy Award for Best Visual Effects|Best Special Effects]] on the film ''[[The Invisible Man Returns]]'' at the [[13th Academy Awards]].<ref name="Oscars1941">{{Cite web|url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/13th-winners.html |title=The 13th Academy Awards (1941) Nominees and Winners |accessdate=2013-06-18|work=oscars.org}}</ref> He worked on more than 90 films during his career.

